9. Barker CM. Models and Surveillance Systems to Detect and Predict West Nile Virus Outbreaks. J Med Entomol. 2019 Sep 24. pii: tjz150. doi: 10.1093/jme/tjz150. [Epub ahead of print]; https://doi.org/10.1093/jme/tjz150.
